Color in live not recorded. Color in alcohol (see 
Figure 3
) brown, with the head, opercular region and tail darker, a small, ovate dark blotch at the dorsal contour under the rays 20–23, and narrow dark streaks on both the dorsal and ventral contours running out the caudal-fin base.
